<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM10.8">
<l>maḻaiyē maḻaiyē maṇpuṟam pūciyuḷ ḷāyniṉṟa</l>
<l>meḻukūṟṟi ṉāṟpō lūṟṟunal vēṅkaṭat tuḷniṉṟa</l>
<l>aḻakap pirāṉār tammaiyeṉ neñcat takappaṭat</l>
<l>taḻuvaniṉ ṟeṉṉait tataittikkoṇ ṭūṟṟavum vallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Handsome Lord who stands inside the good Vēṅkaṭam casts [me] away</l>
<l>just as one coats the outer part [of a statue] with earth and casts away the wax inside:</l>
<l>O clouds! O clouds! Can you pour, [placing] me close [to Him]</l>
<l>[causing me] to remain embracing [Him the way I do] inside my heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
